
1/run paremd script  , to obtain gro et tpr   from xml + parm7
2/ run this commmand to obtain tpr :    gmx grompp -f file.mdp -c *.gro -p *.top -o *.tpr
2/convert the dcd traj to xtc with gromacs modif , modify and run gromacs...py
!! because of diff in def of box matrix between openmm and gromacs ; 
!! openmm consider values close to zero (like 1e-16)  , but gromcas needs to be zeros

3/ gmx make_ndx -f pthrp.gro -o index.ndx   r resid   
!! i recommand to use the center of mass and search for closest residue to the center( python3 center_of_mass.py)
4/  no jump : gmx trjconv -s pthrp.tpr -f  trj_gromacs.xtc  -o trj_nojump.xtc -pbc nojump
5/ centering around the center of mass gmx trjconv -s pthrp.tpr -f  trj_nojump.xtc  -o trj_center.xtc -pbc mol -center -ur compact -n index.ndx   21 0  

6/ visualize : vmd *.parm7  *.xtc ( always)
